name: RCNZ Gorilla With A Brick
description:
Following on from RCNZ Dumb Monkey, this time I smashed together a pile of photorealistic models and the awesome noise offset model to make another mix!

The SD-v2 (840k) VAE is baked into the originals, and all are pruned to fp16
